  <summary date="2020-04-30T22:12:17Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Turkey Human Rights Promotion Act of 2019

This bill directs the Department of State to provide assistance to civil society organizations in Turkey that (1) work to secure the release of prisoners of conscience and political prisoners in Turkey, or (2) provide support and post-incarceration assistance for such prisoners.</summary>
